product_basic_info.description: A wise man once said, “A phone is not a phone until it’s an iPhone.” And that’s the reason you should totally grab this newest entrant in the market, iPhone 6s from Apple to your gadget collection right away. 3D Touch This Multi-touch feature allows you to explore a new dimension by subtly tapping, pinching and swiping the functions, thus making it a user-friendly option. Performance Equipped with a smart 64-bit A9 chip, along with iOS 9 processor, this phone allows you to experience faster and smoother performance. Display Size With a display size of 11.93 cm (4.7 inches), this phone allows you to watch a movie or read something on it clearly. Storage The internal memory of 64 GB and 2 GB RAM will enable you to store a lot of files without having to keep deleting any. Camera The 12-megapixel camera allows you to take sharp and detailed pictures with high resolution. Also, selfies won’t be the same anymore with the 5-megapixel FaceTime HD camera making you look good. You can also click live photos on this phone, and not miss a single moment. Design Enwrapped in an alloy of aluminium, and glass, this rose gold phone is not just durable, but also boasts a sleek and stylish design. Security The fingerprint sensor ensures that your phone is protected at all times, while also making locking and unlocking it easy.
product_basic_info.title: Apple iPhone 6s (Rose Gold, 64 GB)

product_basic_info.description: A premium phone that brings out the best of the smartphone world, puts it together in a beautiful package and presents it to you on a fully functional platter, the iPhone 5 is yet another success story of Apple. The Best Your Eye Can See A 4 inch touchscreen that has so many pixels that the human eye cannot distinguish amongst them, the iPhone Retina Display ensures that you fall for the clear, crisp and bright colors like no other smartphone can reproduce, hook, line and sinker. The capacitive touchscreen is just the right size to fit into the palm, making everything seem better with every blink of the eye. Smooth operations Optimized solely for the iPhone and created to look and perform the best, the iOS 6 operating system combines convenience and functionality with great looks without making life any more complicated than it has to be. Picture Perfect A photographer’s delight, the iPhone 5’s iSight 8 megapixel camera that comes with LED flash reproduces life in bright, bold colors. The 1.2 megapixel secondary camera makes Facetime with a loved one easier and with full HD recording and playback, the iPhone surpasses expectations when it comes to capturing and preserving moments as life flits past. The phone also holds on to capture information to let you know which photo was clicked when without you having to rack your brains. Customized Processor With an A6 chip processor that has been custom-created for the iPhone 5, watch the applications you launch on the operating system perform like butter on toast. Better graphics, faster processing of any application and anything more that you can think of, all with the best of power management possible. Beautiful Technology As always, Apple presents a machine that is crafted to appeal to the eye, with a sleek design that will capture hearts - owner’s pride, neighbour’s envy indeed.
product_basic_info.title: Apple iPhone 5 (Black, 16 GB)

Faster Rendering of Graphics With an A6 chip processor that has been custom-created for the iPhone 5, watch the applications you launch on the operating system perform like butter on toast. Better graphics and faster processing of any application, all with the best of power management possible.

product_basic_info.description: iPhone has a charm that wins the heart of almost every smartphone user. Take this Apple iPhone 5S for instance. Its seamless performance and multiple features will make you a pro at multitasking and leave you amazed with its efficacy. Processor and OS This smart Apple phone is equipped with a powerful A7 chip processor which ensures high performance. It’s based on a 64-bit Architecture and is loaded with an M7 Motion Coprocessor to detect motion-oriented files, thereby, allowing you to enjoy watching HD videos and play games with 3D effects without any glitch. The phone operates on iOS 7 which lets you use the features like AirDrop and Control Centre, and switch from one app to another easily.  Display This single-SIM handset has a wide 10.16 cm screen. It has a Retina Display which is fingerprint-resistant, responds to multi-touch and gives you a 360-degree readability. Battery Life It is powered by a Li-Ion battery with a capacity of up to 1560 mAh. You can use multiple apps without being concerned about the power draining out. Camera This multimedia phone has an 8 MP primary camera with a dual LED flash to capture bright images, and a 1.2 MP selfie camera too. You can record HD videos, edit images, and capture pictures in Panoramic mode as well. Additional Features Other features to look out for in this smartphone are Fingerprint Identity Sensor, proximity sensor, 3-axis gyro sensor, geo-tagging, slow-motion video, Hybrid IR Filter, ambient light sensor and capacitive touch screen.
